## Context

Jake OS is a Flask SPA at `/root/jake_desktop/`. The file `jake_desktop/static/js/criativos.js` already exists (~365 lines, commit e627b3b). You need to replace the last 5 stub functions with real implementations using the Edit tool.

## Task 11: Replace remaining stubs in criativos.js

The current remaining stubs look like this (exact match near the end of the file):

```javascript
  function bindResultadoAcoes() {}
  function bindAbas() {}
  function bindHistoricoEvents() {}
  function carregarPastas() {}
