## Steps

1. Read `/root/jake_desktop/static/js/criativos.js` to find the exact 5 stub lines.

2. Use the Edit tool to replace:
```javascript
  function bindResultadoAcoes() {}
  function bindAbas() {}
  function bindHistoricoEvents() {}
  function carregarPastas() {}
  function carregarHistorico() {}
```
with the full implementation above.

3. Verify Flask still works:
```bash
fuser -k 5050/tcp 2>/dev/null; sleep 1
cd /root/jake_desktop && nohup /root/jake_desktop/venv/bin/python app.py > /tmp/jake_flask.log 2>&1 &
sleep 4 && curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" http://localhost:5050/login
```
Expected: `200`

4. Check the log has no errors:
```bash
tail -10 /tmp/jake_flask.log
```
Expected: Flask running without Python errors.

5. Commit:
```bash
cd /root/jake_desktop && git add static/js/criativos.js
git commit -m "feat: criativos.js — resultado, histórico e pastas completos"
```

